    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>This plugin hide widgets on specified pages. Adds checkboxes to each widget to either show or hide it on every site page.</p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload <code>display-widgets.php</code> to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> directory</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress</li>\n<li>Go to the &#8216;Widgets&#8217; menu and show the options panel for the widget you would like to hide.</li>\n<li>Select either &#8216;Show on Checked&#8217; or &#8216;Hide on Checked&#8217; from the drop-down and check the boxes.</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release.</li>\n</ul>\n"
